description: Returns a list of the dashboards for your account. If you include DashboardNamePrefix, only those dashboards with names starting with the prefix are listed. Otherwise, all dashboards in your account are listed. ListDashboards returns up to 1000 results on one page. If there are more than 1000 dashboards, you can call ListDashboards again and include the value you received for NextToken in the first call, to receive the next 1000 results.

nested_items.name: DashboardArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the dashboard.

nested_items.name: LastModified
nested_items.description: The time stamp of when the dashboard was last modified, either by an API call or through the console. This number is expressed as the number of milliseconds since Jan 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC.

nested_items.name: Size
nested_items.description: The size of the dashboard, in bytes.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token that marks the start of the next batch of returned results.
